WEBVTT

00:01.434 --> 00:03.302
(OPENING THEME PLAYING)

00:30.897 --> 00:33.765
The perfect dinner,
the perfect present,

00:33.767 --> 00:36.835
the perfect Valentine's Day
for your father, little one.

00:36.837 --> 00:38.537
When you've been married
as long as we have,

00:38.539 --> 00:41.306
it's important to keep
the romance alive.

00:41.308 --> 00:44.009
(SIGHS) Oh, man, what a day!

00:44.011 --> 00:45.811
Hi, honey. (KISSES)

00:45.813 --> 00:48.213
Don't forget to kiss
the baby, Mister Man.

00:48.215 --> 00:49.948
(YELLING) Let me go!

00:49.950 --> 00:53.218
There's my little man.
Come here, slugger.

00:53.220 --> 00:55.220
Ew, no, stop!

00:55.222 --> 00:58.390
I am not your baby,
and you two are not married.

00:58.392 --> 01:01.893
I don't know why
you are acting like this,
but it is really weird!

01:01.895 --> 01:03.929
Aw! So sweet.

01:03.931 --> 01:06.298
Look at how excited
he is to see you.

01:06.300 --> 01:08.567
-(BABY CRYING)
-Come here, little man.

01:08.569 --> 01:10.068
It's time for your bottle.

01:10.070 --> 01:12.003
I do not want a...

01:12.405 --> 01:13.839
Hmm...

01:17.043 --> 01:18.977
What's all this?

01:18.979 --> 01:20.412
(GROWLING)

01:20.414 --> 01:24.182
Ha! You all like,
"My man forgot
Valentine's Day."

01:24.184 --> 01:28.086
No way, Jose,
I got something
super special planned.

01:28.088 --> 01:30.055
-You do?
-You know it.

01:30.057 --> 01:33.024
It's Valentine's time!

01:33.026 --> 01:34.593
(BELL RINGING)

01:34.595 --> 01:36.328
What is this, Cyborg?

01:36.330 --> 01:39.364
We're celebrating
Valentine's Day
the best way possible,

01:39.366 --> 01:41.466
in a classroom environment,
baby!

01:41.468 --> 01:42.968
-(CHEERING)
-(LAUGHING)

01:42.970 --> 01:45.537
-Yes!
-Whoo!

01:45.539 --> 01:47.539
-Mr. Cyborg?
-Yes, Star.

01:47.541 --> 01:49.441
May we pass out the cards now?

01:49.443 --> 01:52.277
Does everyone have
their folded paper envelops
taped to their desk?

01:52.279 --> 01:53.345
I sure do.

01:53.347 --> 01:55.147
I spent all night on this.

01:56.582 --> 01:58.950
Then let's hand out
our Valentines.

02:08.995 --> 02:11.797
Wait, you got everyone
the same cards?

02:11.799 --> 02:14.366
-Of course.
-But today is supposed
to be our day.

02:14.368 --> 02:16.334
You don't want to hurt
someone's feelings, do you?

02:16.336 --> 02:19.371
-Wait, you didn't get
cards for everyone?
-No.

02:19.373 --> 02:21.206
You didn't get me a card?

02:21.208 --> 02:23.141
I just got one for my husband.

02:23.143 --> 02:26.912
(BAWLING) I feel so alone.

02:26.914 --> 02:30.115
It's okay, buddy.
It doesn't mean
she doesn't love you.

02:30.117 --> 02:31.516
I don't love him!

02:31.518 --> 02:32.918
I only love you!

02:32.920 --> 02:35.153
Are you trying to ruin
his Valentine's Day?

02:35.155 --> 02:36.421
Unbelievable.

02:36.423 --> 02:38.390
-Honey, wait.
-(SLAMS DOOR)

02:38.392 --> 02:40.725
ALL: Ooh!

02:43.796 --> 02:46.364
-You okay?
-Sorry about all that.

02:46.366 --> 02:49.568
We are here for you,
"Sister's Before the Misters."
(CHEERING)

02:49.570 --> 02:52.170
Yeah, "Girls Rule,
Boys Drool," and all that.

02:53.573 --> 02:55.807
(GIGGLING)

02:55.809 --> 02:58.777
Again, this whole thing
is ridiculous!

02:58.779 --> 03:01.580
Let me go and stop pretending
I'm your baby!

03:01.582 --> 03:03.849
Sorry, he's been
so fussy today.

03:03.851 --> 03:06.284
He hates it when his daddy
and I are fighting.

03:06.286 --> 03:08.053
You're not married!

03:08.055 --> 03:09.254
Poor little guy.

03:09.256 --> 03:10.922
I am not a baby!

03:10.924 --> 03:12.657
He probably needs
to be changed.

03:12.659 --> 03:13.992
No, I don't.

03:13.994 --> 03:15.861
Don't you dare!

03:17.163 --> 03:18.230
No!

03:18.232 --> 03:20.098
(STRAINING)

03:20.100 --> 03:23.535
Oh, my! That is quite
the soggy diaper.

03:23.537 --> 03:25.804
(GROANS) What do you expect?

03:25.806 --> 03:27.839
They have that bottle
in my mouth all day.

03:27.841 --> 03:30.141
Okay, sweetie, almost done.

03:30.143 --> 03:31.243
Leave me alone!

03:31.245 --> 03:35.113
Leave me...
Ah! That feels
so much better.

03:35.115 --> 03:36.715
(SNORES)

03:37.383 --> 03:39.451
You are the good mother.

03:39.453 --> 03:41.119
(BAWLING)

03:46.325 --> 03:49.294
I thought you said a bath
will make him feel better,
Beast Boy.

03:49.296 --> 03:51.062
I know what will cheer him up.

03:52.965 --> 03:57.168
-How is that?
-(SOBBING) Super fresh.

03:57.170 --> 03:59.237
Then stop crying.

03:59.239 --> 04:05.644
I can't. Jinx is so mad at me
and I don't understand why.

04:05.646 --> 04:07.045
Well, of course you don't.

04:07.047 --> 04:09.648
Nothing makes sense
on Valentine's Day.

04:09.650 --> 04:11.449
I know what you need, bro,

04:11.451 --> 04:14.219
you needs to up
your romance game.

04:14.221 --> 04:15.754
Look at yourself.

04:15.756 --> 04:17.622
You need to make an effort
and get some new clothes.

04:17.624 --> 04:19.224
But I'm mostly robot.

04:19.226 --> 04:20.559
I don't wear clothes.

04:20.561 --> 04:21.960
Exactamundo.

04:21.962 --> 04:23.595
Beast Boy,
you know what time it is?

04:23.597 --> 04:24.663
Oh, yeah.

04:24.665 --> 04:26.598
BOTH: Make over time!

04:26.600 --> 04:28.199
(UPBEAT MUSIC PLAYING)

04:30.803 --> 04:32.571
(HAIR DRYER WHIRRING)

04:37.443 --> 04:38.743
(SCREAMING)

04:45.651 --> 04:46.952
You sure this is right?

04:46.954 --> 04:49.187
Yeah! Haven't you ever
seen any movies?

04:49.189 --> 04:51.523
And besides,
you look fabulous.

04:51.525 --> 04:53.024
(GASPS)

04:53.026 --> 04:55.126
-(CHEERING)
-(LAUGHING)

04:55.128 --> 04:56.194
That's what's up.

04:58.631 --> 05:00.332
(LAUGHING)

05:00.334 --> 05:02.033
What's going on?

05:02.035 --> 05:03.535
Jinx? Jinx!

05:03.537 --> 05:05.303
It's not what it looks like.

05:05.305 --> 05:06.838
So, you're not having
the best time ever
with your friends

05:06.840 --> 05:08.673
and not thinking
about me at all?

05:08.675 --> 05:10.108
No! I mean, yes. I mean...

05:10.110 --> 05:12.544
We can't have one day
be about us?

05:12.546 --> 05:13.678
Jinx!

05:13.680 --> 05:15.280
I did this for you!

05:15.282 --> 05:16.781
Oh, I can't win.

05:16.783 --> 05:18.550
Not in that dress, you can't.

05:18.552 --> 05:19.684
Cuts you all wrong...

05:19.686 --> 05:21.419
-Around the waist.
-(GRUNTS)

05:21.421 --> 05:22.554
Forget the dress!

05:22.556 --> 05:24.389
How am I gonna get Jinx back?

05:24.391 --> 05:26.758
There is only one way.

05:26.760 --> 05:30.228
You must journey
to the land of last minute
Valentine's gifts.

05:30.230 --> 05:33.732
You must collect
three magic,
cliched objects of love.

05:33.734 --> 05:35.800
<i>Flowers, chocolates,</i>
<i>and a teddy bear.</i>

05:35.802 --> 05:37.235
<i>And along the way,</i>

05:37.237 --> 05:39.304
<i>you will need to display</i>
<i>virtues of thoughtfulness,</i>

05:39.306 --> 05:40.872
<i>effort and sacrifice.</i>

05:40.874 --> 05:42.474
Thoughtfulness, effort,
sacrifice. Got it.

05:42.476 --> 05:44.576
Will guys watch
the baby for me?

05:44.578 --> 05:48.580
Now that he is gone,
can we just drop this whole
fake marriage and baby thing?

05:48.582 --> 05:51.816
Oh, the little baby
is the fussy.

05:51.818 --> 05:54.119
Oh, we better swaddle him.

05:54.121 --> 05:56.788
-No!
-Hold still, baby.

05:56.790 --> 05:59.257
(STRUGGLING)
Let me out of here!

05:59.259 --> 06:02.594
I can't move in this.
It's hugging me so tight.

06:02.596 --> 06:05.463
And making me...
So cozy, ah...

06:05.465 --> 06:07.899
I am just gonna... (SNORING)

06:10.569 --> 06:12.737
(ROMANTIC MUSIC PLAYING)

06:15.541 --> 06:17.909
This place is so romantic.

06:19.845 --> 06:23.314
Wow, thanks for the lift,
handsome gondola man.

06:23.316 --> 06:24.382
Mmm...

06:28.621 --> 06:30.288
That must be the flower.

06:33.392 --> 06:37.028
If you wish to pick me,
you must answer one question.

06:37.030 --> 06:39.364
You mean a riddle?
Cool! Riddle me up.

06:39.366 --> 06:41.666
Does this color look good
on my petals?

06:41.668 --> 06:42.934
Is that the riddle?

06:42.936 --> 06:45.070
Sure, it looks fine, let's go.

06:45.072 --> 06:47.105
(SOBBING)

06:47.107 --> 06:49.474
What? I said you look fine.

06:49.476 --> 06:52.644
-(SOBBING LOUDER)
-Wow, I'm just saying
it doesn't matter.

06:52.646 --> 06:54.312
No one cares
what you look like.

06:54.314 --> 06:55.914
(CONTINUES SOBBING)

06:55.916 --> 06:57.816
Why are you acting like this?

07:00.619 --> 07:02.053
Hey, hey, hey, hey, hey.

07:02.055 --> 07:05.090
I'm sorry,
I wasn't being thoughtful.

07:05.925 --> 07:07.358
Your petals are perfect.

07:07.993 --> 07:09.394
(GASPS) You think so?

07:09.396 --> 07:12.597
I do. The color really
complements your stem.

07:12.599 --> 07:14.265
Mmm... You noticed.

07:14.267 --> 07:17.068
And don't think I didn't see
that new stamen.

07:17.070 --> 07:19.370
(GIGGLES) I got them on sale.

07:19.372 --> 07:22.440
Could have fooled me,
you look like a million bucks.

07:22.442 --> 07:23.742
You are worthy.

07:23.744 --> 07:26.578
Pick me and let us bring
joy to your loved one.

07:26.580 --> 07:27.846
(SNIP)

07:31.550 --> 07:35.086
"Only one box of chocolates
will win the heart
of your true love."

07:35.088 --> 07:37.288
Hmm, they all look
the same to me.

07:41.694 --> 07:42.827
Eh, this one's fine.

07:42.829 --> 07:44.562
-(CLOCK TICKING)
-No.

07:44.564 --> 07:45.864
Jinx is the best,

07:45.866 --> 07:47.565
she deserves the best.

07:47.567 --> 07:49.400
(EXPLOSION)

07:49.402 --> 07:51.236
Whoa, I should have known.

07:51.238 --> 07:53.438
Picking the easiest gift
is a ticking time bomb.

07:53.440 --> 07:55.473
I have to put some effort
on this one.

07:58.010 --> 07:59.410
That's the one for her.

08:01.313 --> 08:02.380
(EXPLOSION)

08:03.716 --> 08:05.283
(EXPLOSIONS)

08:10.189 --> 08:11.256
There it is!

08:14.527 --> 08:16.461
-(EXPLOSIONS)
-(YELLING)

08:16.463 --> 08:17.996
(SCREAMING)

08:22.334 --> 08:23.835
Totally worth it.

08:24.870 --> 08:27.405
Phew! All I need now
is a teddy bear.

08:29.141 --> 08:30.575
Sure is dark in here.

08:34.847 --> 08:36.214
Aw, so cute.

08:36.216 --> 08:38.116
You're gonna get some
snuggles, buddy.

08:41.220 --> 08:42.387
(GROWLING)

08:42.389 --> 08:43.755
(SCREAMING)

08:43.757 --> 08:45.824
-(GROWLING)
-(GROANING)

08:52.631 --> 08:54.032
(TEDDY BEAR YELPS)

08:54.800 --> 08:56.067
(SQUAWKING)

08:58.637 --> 09:03.441
So, I got you some stuff
'cause I love you
and everything.

09:06.111 --> 09:08.880
<i>♪ Girl you're so amazing</i>
<i>Girl you're so amazing</i>

09:08.882 --> 09:10.181
<i>♪ Yeah...</i>

09:10.183 --> 09:12.851
<i>♪ Like a suit that's</i>
<i>tailor made</i>

09:12.853 --> 09:15.587
<i>♪ Baby I could</i>
<i>wear you everyday</i>

09:16.689 --> 09:20.191
<i>♪ All I want to do, do...</i>

09:20.193 --> 09:22.360
<i>♪ I just thought</i>
<i>I'll let you know</i>

09:22.362 --> 09:24.429
<i>♪ I just thought</i>
<i>I'd let you know</i>

09:24.431 --> 09:26.664
<i>♪ All I want is you</i>

09:26.666 --> 09:27.732
<i>♪ All I want is you</i>

09:27.734 --> 09:29.100
<i>♪ All I want is you</i>

09:29.102 --> 09:31.202
<i>♪ All I want is you</i>

09:31.204 --> 09:34.072
<i>♪ All I want is you, you, you</i>

09:34.074 --> 09:35.773
<i>♪ All I want is you ♪</i>

09:35.775 --> 09:37.375
(BOTH MUMBLING)

09:38.611 --> 09:40.778
(BOTH GIGGLING)

09:40.780 --> 09:42.413
(BOTH EXCLAIMING)

09:42.415 --> 09:43.481
-CYBORG: Little more,
little more.
-(WATCH BEEPING)

09:45.117 --> 09:46.951
Okay, wrap it up, lovebirds.

09:46.953 --> 09:49.854
Friends, you have repaired
your romance.

09:49.856 --> 09:51.656
Yeah, we did.

09:51.658 --> 09:54.225
And all it took
was a little thought,
effort, and sacrifice.

09:54.227 --> 09:56.227
(ELECTRICITY BUZZING)

09:56.229 --> 09:59.097
So, I guess now we know
what it's like to be married
on Valentine's Day.

09:59.099 --> 10:01.099
-Terrible!
-Super terrible.

10:01.101 --> 10:03.434
Let's never pretend
to be married again.

10:09.642 --> 10:13.077
-(GROANS)
Will somebody change me?
-(BABY CRYING)

10:16.615 --> 10:18.616
(THEME MUSIC PLAYING)
